
'''= RIPESS is an intercontinental network that connects social and solidarity economy networks  throughout the world.'''

URL = http://www.ripess.org/  


=Description=

"As a network of networks, it brings together continental networks, that in turn bring together national and sectoral networks.  RIPESS believes in the importance of global solidarity in order to build and strengthen an economy that puts people and planet front and center. From Lima to Quebec, from Dakar to Luxembourg, RIPESS organizes global forums every four years and is a nexus for learning, information sharing and collaboration."
(http://www.ripess.org/about-us/?lang=en)


